wiki.summary: On “ALWAYS DO,“ The Kid LAROI narrates about how even though he and his lover have their differences, they will always return to each other just as they always do. The track was first previewed on an Instagram live by engineering collaborator Donn Robb, then later by the owner of Grade A label, Lil Bibby, and once again in a Rolling Loud Twitch Live Interview with DJ Scheme. The track released on LAROI’s F*CK LOVE (SAVAGE). Read more on Last.fm.
